name: Shinobi of the Predator's Web
description: Having learned to work side-by-side with fruitsippers to achieve their goals, the Shinobi of the Predator's Web are known for cheffin up the good shit. That good good. Yeah. Now experienced navigators that captain liquefaction-based transport systems, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
